name: UnifiedPackage
description: Contains various data types, depending on the usage.

name: BuildInfo
description: Contains developer export information.

name: Chunk
description: The header for a chunk block.

name: DM_WMK_Info
description: Possibly leftover from development. (DSF)

name: ExportedMissionChunk
description: Contains exported mission data.

name: ExportedMissionSummary
description: Contains data in which the game should handle this mission, such as what city to play in.

name: ExportedMissionObjects
description: Contains data for positioning objects and defining actors in a mission.

name: ExportedMissionPropHandles
description: Unknown. Possibly deprecated.

name: ExportedMissionRoot
description: Exported mission data for Driver: Parallel Lines.

name: FontData
description: Contains textures used for fonts.

name: FING
description: Unknown purpose in Driver: Parallel Lines.

name: FontContainer
description: Contains data pertaining to fonts.

name: FontDefinition
description: Contains font definition data in Driver: San Francisco.

name: LEAT
description: Unknown purpose in Driver: Parallel Lines.

name: LogicExportData
description: Contains all of the logic data (definitions, properties, etc).

name: LogicExportNodesChunk
description: Contains logic node definitions and properties.

name: LogicExportNodeDefinitionsTable
description: Contains definitions for mission logic.

name: LENE
description: Unknown purpose in Driver: Parallel Lines.

name: LogicExportPropertiesTable
description: Contains properties associated with each definition.

name: LEPS
description: Unknown purpose in Driver: Parallel Lines.

name: LogicExportSoundBank
description: Contains sound id's to be used in the logic data.

name: LogicExportStringCollection
description: Contains strings associated with the logic data.

name: LogicExportWireCollections
description: Contains wires that link logic nodes together.

name: ModelPackagePC
description: Contains various models and textures. (Driv3r)

name: ModelPackageX
description: Contains various models and textures. (DPL, DSF)

name: MRRD
description: Unknown in DPL *_missions.sp (some sort of flags table?)

name: ReflectionsMenuDataChunk
description: Contains data for handling all GUI-related data.

name: ReflectionsMenuDataPackage
description: Contains data pertaining to the GUI (main menu, pause menu, etc)

name: CharacterSkeletons
description: Contains character skeletons for the male and female models.

name: StandaloneTextures
description: Contains standalone texture Ids.

name: VehicleHierarchy
description: Contains vehicle hierarchy information.

name: ExtraCharacterData
description: Contains character model and texture data.
